translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ノアとサテラの話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Noah and Satella's conversation

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ノアとセックス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sex with Noah

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海４日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 4th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海獣レイドボスが現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A sea beast raid boss appears

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 逃げ切れない、覚悟して戦う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We can't escape, prepare yourself and fight

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle begins

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海獣を撃退した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Repelled the sea beast

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遠くに謎の島を発見する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Discovered a mysterious island in the distance

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 謎の島に上陸する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Landed on the mysterious island

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 果物いっぱい食べるが・・罠だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ate lots of fruit... but it was a trap

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モンスターが現れた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A monster appeared

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食中毒で痺れているランス達に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and others are numb from food poisoning,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モンスターが襲ってきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster attacked

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか倒して島を脱出
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow defeated it and escaped the island

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 幾多の冒険を重ね魔物界側に入った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After many adventures, entered the monster world side

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海６日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 6th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 満ち潮が消滅してもおかしくない時期になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's the time when the high tide might disappear

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いざという時の為に陸地側に寄っておくか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Should we get close to the land side just in case?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海岸沿いを移動中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Moving along the coast

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵に見つかってしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Spotted by monster soldiers

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あわてて上陸、追いかけて戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hurriedly landed, chased and fought

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵に逃げられ援軍を呼ばれ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldier escaped and called reinforcements...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか全滅させた・・船に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow annihilated them all... returning to the ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 危険だが・・沖合を進もう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's dangerous, but let's proceed offshore

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 沖合を進む・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Proceeding offshore...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ホルスが偵察機的に飛んで周囲を調べる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus flies around like a reconnaissance aircraft to investigate the surroundings

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ウィリス、フェリスを呼び出す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Call Willis and Felis

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海７日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 7th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最後の魔法電話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The last magic phone call

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ノアが嵐を察知する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Noah senses a storm

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 嵐になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It turned into a storm

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 激しい嵐が船に襲いかかる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A fierce storm attacks the ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大波は防いだが、嵐は続く・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We defended against the big waves, but the storm continues...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海７日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 7th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サンセット号が見えない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Sunset ship is nowhere to be seen

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 健太郎を拾う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Kentaro

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遭難したサンセット号を探しに行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go search for the stranded Sunset ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サンセット号は捜さない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do not search for the Sunset ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 先に進む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Move forward

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 漂流していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Was drifting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あてな２号を助ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Atena No. 2

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 漂流していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Was drifting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ロッキーを助ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Rocky

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 日照り
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Drought

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食料が不足している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Food supplies are running low

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城の事を心配していたが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were worried about Rance Castle, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フェリスは情報を知っていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Felis already knew the information

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸地点の近くに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We came near the landing point

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２カ所の可能性があるが確定は出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are two possible locations but can't be certain

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その中間地点を目指す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Head towards the midpoint between them

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸地点に近づいた時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When approaching the landing site

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 満ち潮の終わりが来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The end of the high tide has come

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海が消える前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before the sea disappears,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか上陸に成功した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Managed to land somehow

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界の海岸に上陸したランス達。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others landed on the coast of the monster world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸した直後です。夕方のイメージぐらいで
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just after landing. Imagine it to be around evening.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう海は無い、帰る事は出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The sea is gone, we can't go back

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: キバ子あたりが森から取ってきた食材でみんな夕食にする
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone has dinner with ingredients Kibako got from the forest

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魚ばかりで飽きていたしね、と少しほんわり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were getting tired of just fish, so it's a bit comforting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 火炊いて大丈夫か・・魔軍にばれたりしないか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is it okay to start a fire... won't the demon army find out?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 果物いっぱい食べるが・・罠だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ate lots of fruit... but it was a trap

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モンスターが現れた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A monster appeared

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食中毒で痺れているランス達に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and others are numb from food poisoning,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モンスターが襲ってきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster attacked

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか倒して島を脱出
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow defeated it and escaped the island

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 幾多の冒険を重ね魔物界側に入った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After many adventures, entered the monster world side

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海６日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 6th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 満ち潮が消滅してもおかしくない時期になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's the time when the high tide might disappear

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いざという時の為に陸地側に寄っておくか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Should we get close to the land side just in case?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海岸沿いを移動中
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Moving along the coast

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵に見つかってしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Spotted by monster soldiers

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あわてて上陸、追いかけて戦闘
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hurriedly landed, chased and fought

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵に逃げられ援軍を呼ばれ・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldier escaped and called reinforcements...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか全滅させた・・船に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow annihilated them all... returning to the ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 危険だが・・沖合を進もう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's dangerous, but let's proceed offshore

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 沖合を進む・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Proceeding offshore...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ホルスが偵察機的に飛んで周囲を調べる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus flies around like a reconnaissance aircraft to investigate the surroundings

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ウィリス、フェリスを呼び出す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Call Willis and Felis

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海７日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 7th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最後の魔法電話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The last magic phone call

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ノアが嵐を察知する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Noah senses a storm

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 嵐になった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It turned into a storm

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 激しい嵐が船に襲いかかる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A fierce storm attacks the ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大波は防いだが、嵐は続く・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We defended against the big waves, but the storm continues...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 航海７日目の朝
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Morning of the 7th day of the voyage

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サンセット号が見えない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Sunset ship is nowhere to be seen

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 健太郎を拾う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Kentaro

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遭難したサンセット号を探しに行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Go search for the stranded Sunset ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サンセット号は捜さない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do not search for the Sunset ship

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 先に進む
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Move forward

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 漂流していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Was drifting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あてな２号を助ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Atena No. 2

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 漂流していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Was drifting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ロッキーを助ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescue Rocky

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 日照り
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Drought

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 食料が不足している
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Food supplies are running low

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城の事を心配していたが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were worried about Rance Castle, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フェリスは情報を知っていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Felis already knew the information

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸地点の近くに来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We came near the landing point

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２カ所の可能性があるが確定は出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are two possible locations but can't be certain

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その中間地点を目指す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Head towards the midpoint between them

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸地点に近づいた時
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When approaching the landing site

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 満ち潮の終わりが来た
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The end of the high tide has come

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 海が消える前に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before the sea disappears,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか上陸に成功した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Managed to land somehow

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物界の海岸に上陸したランス達。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others landed on the coast of the monster world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 上陸した直後です。夕方のイメージぐらいで
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just after landing. Imagine it to be around evening.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう海は無い、帰る事は出来ない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The sea is gone, we can't go back

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: キバ子あたりが森から取ってきた食材でみんな夕食にする
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone has dinner with ingredients Kibako got from the forest

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魚ばかりで飽きていたしね、と少しほんわり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We were getting tired of just fish, so it's a bit comforting

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 火炊いて大丈夫か・・魔軍にばれたりしないか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is it okay to start a fire... won't the demon army find out?
